/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=http://imgur.com/rVhlV0F\u0022 style=\u0022height:416px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=http://imgur.com/GOJIg9g\u0022 style=\u0022height:416px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill do \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E and return to KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas probe core and 5x Docking Ports to enable external tanks, equipment packs\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt also has a Grapple to dock to the side of ships, due to the lack of magnetic skids.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s extremely sensitive on takeoff, so adopt 5-10degrees angle of attack and leave it there, otherwise you won\u0027t get the nose up again and achieve orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2x Puff engines will give extra boost to chase down raiders etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAction groups as follows.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Toggle RAPIERs/Intakes between air breathing and closed cycle\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Toggle rapiers on and off\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Toggle Grapple\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. Toggle docking port\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5. Toggle Puff engines\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHandles like a jackrabbit, and is easy to do high angle of attack manouvers with lower fuel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCraft file is here on kerbalx\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/atassiedevil/Viper-Mk2\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalx.com/atassiedevil/Viper-Mk2\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnjoy!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}